    <string name="trakt_connect_description">Trakt is a platform that does many things, but primarily keeps
        track of TV shows and movies you watch. It integrates with your media center or home theater PC
        to enable scrobbling, so everything is automatic. Some people like to check in from their phone,
        so Trakt enable\'s that too. \n\n If you would like to connect your Trakt account so you can manage your shows from the UpNext
        TV Series Manager app, click the connect button below. You will be redirected to the Trakt website where you will be required
        to authorize the UpNext app. You can revoke the access at any time from your Trakt account.</string>
